River City Ransom , later released as Street Gangs in the PAL regions , is an open world action role - playing beat 'em up video game for the Family Computer / NES .
It was developed by Technōs Japan and originally released in Japan on April 25 , 1989 .
It is the third game in Technos ' Kunio - kun series released for the console , preceded by Renegade and Super Dodge Ball .
Like its predecessors , River City Ransom underwent great changes in its storyline and graphical presentation during its localization in order to make the game more palatable in the Western market .
It was one of the first console games published by North American subsidiary American Technos .
Remakes of the game have been released for the Sharp X68000 , PC - Engine Super CD - ROM² , and Game Boy Advance ( GBA ) .
The NES version was re - released for the Nintendo Wii Virtual Console in 2007 as well as the Nintendo Wii U Virtual Console in October 2015 .
It was also released on the Nintendo 3DS Virtual Console in the PAL Regions in July 25 , 2013 and in North America in November 14 , 2013 .
It was released again on the Nintendo Switch Online Service on it 's launch day , September 18 , 2018 .
